TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Project: 49227 - April 2018 Developed by: C9930462 (Lokesh Bhardwaj) Source qualifier that extracts BR Transactions data from Oracle R12 tables. --Modified to add new fields for project 49269 for July 2018 release
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_AR_PAYMENT_SCHEDULES_ALL

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DISTINCT E.STATUS ACCT_DOC_NUM, D.CLASS, A.DRAWEE_ID CUSTOMER_ACCNT_NAT, HCAS.CUST_ACCT_SITE_ID CUSTOMER_BILL_TO_LOC_NAT, CUSTOMER.PAYER_PARTY_ID AS CUSTOMER_NAT, $$DATASOURCE_NUM_ID AS DATASOURCE_NUM_ID, A.INVOICE_CURRENCY_CODE DOC_CURR_CODE, E.TRANSACTION_HISTORY_ID || '~' || E.CUSTOMER_TRX_ID AS INTEGRATION_ID, A.TRX_DATE INVOICED_DT, A.SET_OF_BOOKS_ID AS LEDGER_NAT, GL.CURRENCY_CODE LOC_CURR_CODE, A.ORG_ID OPERATING_UNIT_ORG_NAT, D.AMOUNT_DUE_ORIGINAL ORIGINAL_AR_DOC_AMT, CASE WHEN D.EXCHANGE_RATE IS NULL THEN D.AMOUNT_DUE_ORIGINAL ELSE D.AMOUNT_DUE_ORIGINAL * D.EXCHANGE_RATE END AS ORIGINAL_AR_LOC_AMT, E.MATURITY_DATE PAYMENT_DUE_DT, 'BR_TRANSACTIONS' AS RECORD_TYPE, D.PAYMENT_SCHEDULE_ID AS REF_DOC_NUM, D.AMOUNT_DUE_REMAINING REMAINING_AR_DOC_AMT, D.ACCTD_AMOUNT_DUE_REMAINING REMAINING_AR_LOC_AMT, A.TRX_NUMBER SALES_INVOICE_NUM, D.ACTUAL_DATE_CLOSED AS TRANSACTION_DT, D.CLASS TRANSACTION_TYPE, A.CUSTOMER_TRX_ID AS CUSTOMER_TRX_ID, A.COMMENTS TRXN_NOTE, A.DOC_SEQUENCE_VALUE DOC_SEQ_VALUE, RBSA.NAME SOURCE_NAME FROM APPS.RA_CUSTOMER_TRX_ALL A, APPS.AR_PAYMENT_SCHEDULES_ALL D, APPS.AR_TRANSACTION_HISTORY_ALL E, APPS.HZ_CUST_ACCOUNTS HZAC, GL_LEDGERS GL, (SELECT MAX(G.PAYER_PARTY_ID) PAYER_PARTY_ID, B.TRXN_REF_NUMBER2 FROM APPS.IBY_FNDCPT_TX_EXTENSIONS B, APPS.IBY_FNDCPT_TX_OPERATIONS F, APPS.IBY_TRXN_SUMMARIES_ALL G WHERE F.TRANSACTIONID = G.TRANSACTIONID(+) AND B.TRXN_EXTENSION_ID = F.TRXN_EXTENSION_ID GROUP BY B.TRXN_REF_NUMBER2) CUSTOMER, APPS.HZ_CUST_SITE_USES_ALL HCSU, APPS.HZ_CUST_ACCT_SITES_ALL HCAS, RA_BATCH_SOURCES_ALL RBSA WHERE 1 = 1 AND GL.LEDGER_ID = A.SET_OF_BOOKS_ID AND A.DRAWEE_ID = HZAC.CUST_ACCOUNT_ID AND A.CUSTOMER_TRX_ID = D.CUSTOMER_TRX_ID AND A.CUSTOMER_TRX_ID = E.CUSTOMER_TRX_ID AND E.CURRENT_RECORD_FLAG = 'Y' AND UPPER(D.CLASS) IN ($$CLASS) AND E.EVENT_ID IS NOT NULL AND CUSTOMER.TRXN_REF_NUMBER2(+) = A.CUSTOMER_TRX_ID -- AND A.TRX_NUMBER = '17027170' AND A.DRAWEE_SITE_USE_ID = HCSU.SITE_USE_ID(+) AND HCAS.CUST_ACCT_SITE_ID = HCSU.CUST_ACCT_SITE_ID AND A.BATCH_SOURCE_ID = RBSA.BATCH_SOURCE_ID(+) AND A.ORG_ID = RBSA.ORG_ID(+)

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Project: 49227 - April 2018 Developed by: C9930462 (Lokesh Bhardwaj) Lookup on Oracle R12 tables to get CUSTOMER_CONTACT_NAT
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_HZ_PARTIES

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT CUSTOMER_CONTACT_NAT as CUSTOMER_CONTACT_NAT, SITE_USE_ID as SITE_USE_ID FROM ( SELECT CUSTOMER_CONTACT_NAT, SITE_USE_ID, LAST_UPDATE_DATE, RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY CUSTOMER_CONTACT_NAT, SITE_USE_ID ORDER BY LAST_UPDATE_DATE DESC) AS RK FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT PP.PARTY_ID AS CUSTOMER_CONTACT_NAT, HCSU.SITE_USE_ID AS SITE_USE_ID, PP.LAST_UPDATE_DATE AS LAST_UPDATE_DATE FROM HZ_CUST_SITE_USES_ALL HCSU, HZ_CUST_ACCT_SITES_ALL HCAS, HZ_CUST_ACCOUNTS_ALL HCA, HZ_PARTY_SITES HPS, HZ_CUSTOMER_PROFILES HCP, HZ_CUST_PROFILE_CLASSES HCPC, HZ_PARTIES HP, HZ_CONTACT_POINTS HPC, HZ_CUST_ACCOUNT_ROLES HCAR, HZ_PARTIES PREL, HZ_PARTIES PP, HZ_RELATIONSHIPS HR, HZ_ROLE_RESPONSIBILITY HRR WHERE 1=1 AND HCAS.CUST_ACCT_SITE_ID = HCSU.CUST_ACCT_SITE_ID AND HCA.CUST_ACCOUNT_ID = HCAS.CUST_ACCOUNT_ID AND HP.PARTY_ID = HPS.PARTY_ID AND HPS.PARTY_SITE_ID = HCAS.PARTY_SITE_ID AND HCSU.SITE_USE_ID = HCP.SITE_USE_ID(+) AND HCP.PROFILE_CLASS_ID = HCPC.PROFILE_CLASS_ID(+) AND HCAR.CUST_ACCT_SITE_ID = HCAS.CUST_ACCT_SITE_ID AND HPC.OWNER_TABLE_ID = HCAR.PARTY_ID AND HPC.STATUS = 'A' AND HCAR.PARTY_ID = HR.PARTY_ID AND UPPER(HCAR.ROLE_TYPE) IN ('$$ROLE_TYPE') AND UPPER(HR.RELATIONSHIP_CODE) IN ('$$RELATIONSHIP_CODE') AND PREL.PARTY_ID = HR.PARTY_ID AND HR.OBJECT_ID = PP.PARTY_ID AND HRR.CUST_ACCOUNT_ROLE_ID = HCAR.CUST_ACCOUNT_ROLE_ID ) HZ_PARTIES ) HZ_PARTIES_RK WHERE RK=1

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Project: 49227 - April 2018 Developed by: C9930462 (Lokesh Bhardwaj) Lookup on Oracle R12 - APPS.RA_CUSTOMER_TRX_ALL table to get BILL_TO_SITE_USE_ID, INVOICE_HDR_ETN_LEDGER
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_RA_CUSTOMER_TRX_ALL

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DISTINCT TRX2.TRX_NUMBER AS TRX_NUMBER, HCP.CUST_ACCOUNT_ID AS CUST_ACCOUNT_ID, TRX2.BILL_TO_SITE_USE_ID AS BILL_TO_SITE_USE_ID, TRX2.ATTRIBUTE9 AS INVOICE_HDR_ETN_LEDGER, TRX2.CT_REFERENCE AS CT_REFERENCE, TRX2.LAST_UPDATE_DATE AS LAST_UPDATE_DATE FROM APPS.RA_CUSTOMER_TRX_ALL TRX2, HZ_CUSTOMER_PROFILES HCP WHERE 1=1 AND TRX2.CT_REFERENCE = TRX2.TRX_NUMBER AND TRX2.BILL_TO_SITE_USE_ID IS NOT NULL AND TRX2.BILL_TO_SITE_USE_ID = HCP.SITE_USE_ID --AND TRX2.TRX_NUMBER = '17005116' --AND HCP.CUST_ACCOUNT_ID = 28228 ORDER BY TRX2.LAST_UPDATE_DATE--

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MAX(E.EVENT_ID) AS EVENT_ID, A.CUSTOMER_TRX_ID AS CUSTOMER_TRX_ID FROM APPS.RA_CUSTOMER_TRX_ALL A, APPS.AR_PAYMENT_SCHEDULES_ALL D, APPS.AR_TRANSACTION_HISTORY_ALL E WHERE 1=1 AND A.CUSTOMER_TRX_ID = D.CUSTOMER_TRX_ID AND A.CUSTOMER_TRX_ID = E.CUSTOMER_TRX_ID AND UPPER(D.CLASS) IN ($$CLASS) AND E.STATUS IN ($$STATUS) AND E.EVENT_ID IS NOT NULL GROUP BY A.CUSTOMER_TRX_ID
